1. *Onoga* dana smo bili svi srećni. (That day we were all happy.)
2. Ona je nekad bila *onoga* mislioca. (She used to be that thinker.)
3. Nisam znao da je to *onoga* čoveka. (I didn't know that it was that man.)
4. Svi smo se sećali *onoga* dana. (We all remembered that day.)
5. *Onog* čoveka nikad nisam sreo. (I have never met that man.)
6. Nije mogao da se seti *onoga*. (He couldn't remember that.)